Hukumar Kula da Yanayin Kasa ta yi hasashen cewa za a yi ruwan sama a yammacin Arizona zuwa kudancin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, wanda ya hada da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake a ranar Litinin da Talata.
