Za a fara watsa shirye-shiryen zaben Trump a birnin Wiling na jihar West Virginia da karfe 7 na yammacin Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018 a lokacin yankin gabashin Amurka.
Za ku iya kallon wannan zaben Trump a West Virginia a raye a YouTube.
A cewar rahotanni da aka samu a makon da ya gabata, Trump ya ce zai zabi Burt Kavana a matsayin babban alkalin kotun kasar, a yayin da aka zarge shi da laifin yin rajistar masu aikata laifuka, kuma majalisar dattawa ta dage zabensa har sai an kammala binciken da 'yan sandan FBI ke yi.
Amma babban manufar wannan tsari na zabe shi ne taimakawa 'yan jam'iyyar Republican wajen samun kuri'u a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba, wanda ya fuskanci wasu rikice-rikice.
