Kafofin yada labarai na kasar sun ce, sabon jirgin ruwan na rundunar sojin ruwan Jamus zai fara aiki ne a shekarar 2014 domin maye gurbin jiragen yakin duniya, amma ba zai fara aiki ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar kudi.
A cewar jaridar Die Zeit daga dan mai magana da yawun sojin, an dage shirin gina "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan sabuwar alama ta Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya a shekarar 2014 a mika wannan jirgin ruwa ga rundunar sojin ruwan kasar, amma batun tsadar kudin da zai yi ya janyo jinkirin wannan babban aikin.
Jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da rundunar ta bayar a shekarar 2007 za su zama na biyu na jerin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
