2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Acehyya na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra ta afkawa kasar a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, inda ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a bakin tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su kuwa a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias dake gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, ta haifar da tsunami da kuma mamaye bakin tekun kudu, inda ta kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Kudancin Sumatra.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a Sumatra, tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 ya lalata kauyuka da dama, ya kashe kusan mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa masarautar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da bala'i, inda mutane suka shiga cikin watan bala'i na 2004 da tsunami.
A wannan karon tsunami ya auku, amma sama da mutane 100 suka mutu sakamakon faduwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
