China na son ta yi wa Amurka wasa da-da-da-da, kuma kasa ta biyu mafi girma a duniya ba ta da nisa da yin hakan nan da nan.
Shiga Washington a kasa ko shiga cikin masu neman, amma a fili suna nuna rashin amincewarsu ga Amurka zai zama matsala ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Har yanzu masana na ganin Beijing na iya taka katunta da kyau, inda yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafawa China cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin kasashen biyu.
Abigail Grace, wata abokiyar bincike kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Amurka wacce ke da tushen tunani, ta ce "Gaskiyar cewa matakin siyasa na gaggawa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da rikice-rikicen tattalin arziki a kowace ƙasa wanda yanzu ya zama mafi haɗari kuma wannan ya bayyana.
Ministan harkokin wajen KAREN ya ce, Syria ta shirya don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira
Syria ta ce a shirye take da 'yan gudun hijirar su koma gida da son rai, kuma ta bukaci a taimaka wajen sake gina kasar da ta shafe sama da shekaru bakwai tana fama da rikici.
Ministan harkokin wajen kasar, Walid Muelim, wanda ke jawabi a babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ya ce halin da ake ciki a kasar na inganta.
Ya ce "yanzu yanayin ya fi na kasa kyau kuma ya fi na tsaro saboda yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da mayar da wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin daidaita yanayin.
An samar da dukkan yanayi domin dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar da suka bar kasar saboda ta'addanci da kuma ayyukan tattalin arziki da suka yi wa rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma aikin su.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun bayan yakin da ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida kuma suna zaune a kasar kuma suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al Muelim ya ce gwamnatin Syria na maraba da taimakon da ake bayarwa don kawo karshen wannan rikici.
Sai dai ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka yi masa ba ko kuma na kasashen da ke taimakawa 'yan tawayen.
Turai za ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Team Europe ta shiga gasar Ryder Cup 2018 inda ta doke Team USA a wasan karshe da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National da ke wajen birnin Paris na Faransa.
A yanzu haka Amurka ta kai wa nahiyar Turai wasa shida a jere kuma ba ta taba lashe kofin Ryder Cup ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kambin gasar ne bayan da dan Denmark Thomas Bjorn ya kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin murkushe Amurka.
Phil Mickelson, tauraron dan wasan Amurka wanda ya yi aiki a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a kan par-3 a kan rami na 16, inda ya buga wa Francesco Molinar.
Molinarri, dan wasan Italiya, ya yi nasara a dukkan wasannin, ya zama na farko daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka tafi 5-0-0 tare da wannan ƙwallon ƙafa tun farkon gasar tun 1979.
Jordan Spieth, dan Amurka, ya sha kashi a hannun Thorbjorn Olesen dan Denmark, wanda ke wasa a matakin ƙasa da 5th na Turai.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, ya doke Ian Poulter na Ingila da ci 2-1 a wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder.
