Yanayin Red Tide: Yanayin ruwan sama ya ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa Red Tide yana raguwa a sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana bayar da rahoton yanayin lalata 'yan wasa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier  wanda ke nuna rashin talauci.
Wani ci gaba ne wanda Red Tide ya shimfiɗa kusan mil 130 na layin tekun daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
Wasu gadaje na iya amfani da su a mil 10 na gabar tekun Hillsborough, amma a wasu wurare ba haka ba a makon da ya gabata.
An gano Red Tide a yankin Pasco
An samu karuwar karuwar ruwa a yankin Pemellas a makon da ya gabata, da kuma karuwar ruwa a yankin Hillsborough, da kuma karuwar ruwa a yankin Manatee, da karuwar ruwa a yankin Sarasota, da karuwar ruwa a yankin Lee, da kuma karuwar ruwa a yankin Collier.
Har yanzu ana samun matsaloli na numfashi a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton matsalar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a makonnin baya.
